    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i cant really get to a doctor right now and it's just a normal headache. i usually take 400mg of advil and it works fine. since my kidney numbers have been stable for months, how much ibuprofen would be safe to take just once to get rid of this pain?",
